<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>notify() in Console.php used str_pad() in case ELEMENT_TEXT, but it doesn't account the length of unicode strings - resulting in wrong lengths and thus moving the line further left into the previous line.</p>

<p>The call to str_pad() should be switched to Zend_Text_MultiByte::strPad()</p>

